Author: FreeHugsFromSenpai
Text: Hey, hang in there!! Sending you virtual hugs, hope your day gets better! Don't be so hard on yourself for breaking routine and eating early - maybe do something relaxing that you enjoy to get your mind off of it? Painting, reading, go for a walk and get some fresh air and sunshine..
